summary: Howdy, commissions are now open~ [[MORE]] To view more of my work please check out my artblog @okuyasusfade. You can contact me...
caption:
Howdy, commissions are now open~ 

To view more of my work please check out my artblog @okuyasusfade. You can contact me here on tumblr or my email zyphrnoiir@gmail.com for questions of any sort.

Commissions take anywhere from 1-2 weeks to complete, I will not start drawing till full payment has been received. I accept payment thru PayPal and Cashapp
Paypal.me/Znni
Cashapp: $Znni

I will not draw:
-anything i find personally gross/triggering (rape, incest, pedophiliac, ect)
-furries (cat girls and such are fine tho)
-mecha
-porn (nudity is ok)
-fetish

I will draw:
-OCs (provide references pls)
-Blood/Mild Gore
-Ship art/Fanart
-I’m pretty reasonable let me know any and all specifics for your request and I will accommodate best I can.

If theres a delays for your commission I will inform you as such, if for some reason I’m unable to complete the request I will provide a full refund.
